INSERT INTO chatter (
                id,
                login,
                name,
                color,
                image,
                total,
                private,
                created_at,
                updated_at
            )
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, 0, false, $6, $7)
            ON CONFLICT (id)
            DO UPDATE SET 
                login = $2,
                name = $3,
                color = $4,
                image = $5,
                updated_at = NOW()
